---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="UNMASK Blueprint Series — Books & Manuals"
  description="The UNMASK Blueprint Series — a three-volume intellectual framework deconstruciting burnout through a Womanist lens. Individual, institutional, and collective recalibration."
  section="st"
  accentColor="teal"
>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-st-gradient"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-teal-DEFAULT"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 70% 40%, rgba(13,148,136,0.09) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-mid relative z-10">
      <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex animate-on-scroll">Publications · 2026</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl text-light font-bold mb-5 animate-on-scroll">
        UNMASK Blueprint<br/>
        <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT">Series.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mb-3 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
        A trilogy for personal, institutional, and collective transformation.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted text-base max-w-2xl mb-6 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
        Published under Nikki Cates LLC and Strategic Transformations, the UNMASK Blueprint trilogy is a
        multi-format intellectual framework — available in print, eBook, and interactive app — that deconstructs
        burnout through a Womanist lens. Each volume builds on the proprietary UNMASK Framework: a diagnostic
        and recalibration methodology that identifies hidden strains and rebuilds authentic leadership.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted text-sm max-w-2xl mb-10 animate-on-scroll italic" style="animation-delay:0.14s">
        The series has garnered acclaim for its blend of structural analysis, spiritual recalibration,
        and practical tools — essential for leaders in nonprofits, higher education, faith-based organizations,
        and mission-driven enterprises.
      </p>
      <a href="https://unmask.nikkicates.com/manual-checkout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-teal animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
        Access the Series →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── THE THREE VOLUMES ─────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="space-y-10">

        <!-- Vol 1 -->
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="md:col-span-2 flex justify-center md:justify-start">
              <div class="w-28 h-40 rounded-md flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center border border-teal-DEFAULT/40 shrink-0 px-2"
                   style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0f4c7a 0%, #0d9488 100%);">
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">DECONSTRUCTION</p>
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">OF THE GRIND</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white/30 my-2"></div>
                <p class="font-body text-white/60 text-xs">UNMASK Vol. 1</p>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-light text-xs mt-1">$24.99</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
              <div>
                <span class="st-tag text-xs mb-2 inline-flex">Volume 1 · Individual Level</span>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-light font-bold">Deconstruction of the Grind</h2>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-DEFAULT text-sm italic mt-1">Reclaiming Sovereign Softness</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-1">by Nikki Cates · 5×8 print ($24.99) · eBook · Interactive App</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Volume 1 centers the individual journey — unmasking internalized performance pressures and reclaiming
                rest as a radical act of self-stewardship. It introduces the
                <span class="text-light font-semibold">Leadership Masking Index (LMI)</span> and challenges the
                "grind" culture that disproportionately affects marginalized leaders.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Moving from <em class="not-italic text-light">"performative survival"</em> to
                <em class="not-italic text-teal-DEFAULT">"liberated softness,"</em> this volume uses narrative vignettes
                and reflective exercises to address identity fragmentation, boundary erosion, and emotional labor —
                grounded in Womanist theology that positions rest as resistance against systemic demands.
              </p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-body text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">Key Diagnostic Tool:</p>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-surface border border-border rounded-md">
                  <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0 font-bold">→</span>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-light text-sm font-semibold">Leadership Masking Index (LMI)</p>
                    <p class="text-muted text-xs">Identifies the masks leaders wear — and the structural conditions demanding they wear them.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs font-semibold italic">
                Early user pilots report 30–50% reductions in self-reported burnout through the LMI frameworks.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-3 md:items-end justify-start">
              <a href="https://unmask.nikkicates.com/manual-checkout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-teal w-full md:w-auto justify-center !text-sm">
                Get Vol. 1 →
              </a>
              <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-outline-teal w-full md:w-auto justify-center !text-sm">
                Bulk / Institutional Inquiry
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <!-- Vol 2 -->
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.08s">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="md:col-span-2 flex justify-center md:justify-start">
              <div class="w-28 h-40 rounded-md flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center border border-teal-DEFAULT/40 shrink-0 px-2"
                   style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0a2d4a 0%, #0f4c7a 50%, #0d9488 100%);">
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">REDESIGNING</p>
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">SYSTEMS</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white/30 my-2"></div>
                <p class="font-body text-white/60 text-xs">UNMASK Vol. 2</p>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-light text-xs mt-1">$59.99</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="st-tag text-xs inline-flex">Volume 2 · Institutional Level</span>
                  <span class="bg-teal-DEFAULT/20 text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-teal-DEFAULT/30">Most Requested</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-light font-bold">Redesigning Systems</h2>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-DEFAULT text-sm italic mt-1">The Institutional Imperative</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-1">by Nikki Cates · 6×9 print ($59.99) · eBook · Interactive App with calculators & scenario planners</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Volume 2 moves to organizational architecture — diagnosing and repairing systemic failures that amplify burnout,
                including authority gaps and AI-accelerated overload. It introduces the
                <span class="text-light font-semibold">Responsibility-Authority Asymmetry (RAA) Index</span> and the
                <span class="text-light font-semibold">AI Acceleration Burnout Index</span>,
                providing metrics for institutional health.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Through the concept of <em class="not-italic text-light">"structural imago"</em> (inherent worth in systems)
                and tools like <span class="text-light font-semibold">The Three Leaks</span> (energy drains in hierarchies),
                this volume shifts from individual coping to collective redesign — with case studies on nonprofits and
                mission-driven teams.
              </p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-body text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">Key Diagnostic Tools:</p>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  {[
                    { tool: 'RAA Index', desc: 'Measures the gap between responsibility assigned and authority granted.' },
                    { tool: 'AI Acceleration Burnout Index', desc: 'Quantifies how AI-era overload compounds existing structural strain.' },
                    { tool: 'The Three Leaks', desc: 'Identifies the three primary energy drains embedded in hierarchical structures.' },
                  ].map((t) => (
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-surface border border-border rounded-md">
                      <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0 font-bold">→</span>
                      <div>
                        <p class="text-light text-xs font-semibold">{t.tool}</p>
                        <p class="text-muted text-xs">{t.desc}</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-3 md:items-end justify-start">
              <a href="https://unmask.nikkicates.com/manual-checkout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-teal w-full md:w-auto justify-center !text-sm">
                Get Vol. 2 →
              </a>
              <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-outline-teal w-full md:w-auto justify-center !text-sm">
                Institutional License Inquiry
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <!-- Vol 3 -->
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.16s">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="md:col-span-2 flex justify-center md:justify-start">
              <div class="w-28 h-40 rounded-md flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center border border-teal-DEFAULT/40 shrink-0 px-2"
                   style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #1a0a2e 40%, #2d1048 75%, #0d9488 100%);">
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">THE SOUL</p>
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">OF THE</p>
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-snug">SYSTEM</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white/30 my-2"></div>
                <p class="font-body text-white/60 text-xs">UNMASK Vol. 3</p>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-light text-xs mt-1">$79.00</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
              <div>
                <span class="st-tag text-xs mb-2 inline-flex">Volume 3 · Collective Level</span>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-light font-bold">The Soul of the System</h2>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-DEFAULT text-sm italic mt-1">Collective Liberation — A Structural Sovereignty Blueprint for the Leader Who Is Done Being the Load Path</p>
                <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-1">by Nikki Cates · 7×10 print ($79.00) · eBook · Interactive App with collaborative modules</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Volume 3 moves to the broader ecosystem — empowering communities through shared recalibration.
                It introduces the <span class="text-light font-semibold">Canary Signal</span> (early warnings of
                collapse) and <span class="text-light font-semibold">Load Path</span> (distributing systemic weight),
                while integrating faith-based and justice-centered strategies for collective resilience.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Drawing on the <em class="not-italic text-light">Greene Legacy</em> (historical Womanist influences)
                and <em class="not-italic text-light">"radical subjectivity" as strategy</em>, this volume addresses
                collective masking in AI-disrupted environments through group exercises designed for educators and empowerers.
              </p>
              <div>
                <p class="font-body text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">Key Concepts:</p>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  {[
                    { tool: 'Canary Signal', desc: 'Detects early-warning signs of collective structural collapse before the breaking point.' },
                    { tool: 'Load Path Analysis', desc: 'Maps how systemic weight is distributed — and redistributed — across the collective.' },
                    { tool: 'Greene Legacy Framework', desc: 'Historical Womanist influences as strategic foundation for collective recalibration.' },
                  ].map((t) => (
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-surface border border-border rounded-md">
                      <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0 font-bold">→</span>
                      <div>
                        <p class="text-light text-xs font-semibold">{t.tool}</p>
                        <p class="text-muted text-xs">{t.desc}</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-3 md:items-end justify-start">
              <a href="https://unmask.nikkicates.com/manual-checkout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-teal w-full md:w-auto justify-center !text-sm">
                Get Vol. 3 →
              </a>
              <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-outline-teal w-full md:w-auto justify-center !text-sm">
                Bulk / Institutional Inquiry
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── GET ALL THREE ─────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-10 bg-[#0c1525] border-y border-border">
    <div class="container-mid text-center animate-on-scroll">
      <p class="font-heading text-xl text-light mb-2">Get the complete series.</p>
      <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-2 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        All three volumes are available in print, eBook, and interactive app formats.
        Individual, team, and institutional licensing available.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted text-xs mb-6 italic">
        In a $5.2 billion mental health app market projected to $17.5 billion by 2030,
        UNMASK stands out by framing burnout as structural injustice — not individual weakness.
      </p>
      <a href="https://unmask.nikkicates.com/manual-checkout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-teal !text-base !py-3.5 !px-8">
        Access the UNMASK Checkout →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── LICENSING ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Licensing</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-light">Deploy UNMASK in Your Organization</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
          The UNMASK Framework is licensable for individual practitioners and institutional deployment.
          All licensing inquiries begin with the Executive Briefing process.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            icon: '👤',
            name: 'Individual License',
            desc: 'Personal use for leaders, coaches, and practitioners. Single-user access to all three volumes — print, eBook, and app — with usage rights for individual client engagements.',
            cta: 'Purchase Individual',
            href: 'https://unmask.nikkicates.com/manual-checkout',
            external: true,
          },
          {
            icon: '👥',
            name: 'Team License',
            desc: 'For organizational teams up to 25 people. Includes facilitation guides, team implementation protocols, and the full suite of diagnostic calculators and scenario planners.',
            cta: 'Inquire About Team',
            href: '/structural-burnout/briefing',
          },
          {
            icon: '🏢',
            name: 'Institutional License',
            desc: 'Enterprise-wide deployment for nonprofits, HBCUs, and mission-driven organizations. Practitioner certification pathway included. Potential for $50K–$300K annual licensing.',
            cta: 'Request Institutional Briefing',
            href: '/structural-burnout/briefing',
          },
        ].map((lic) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover text-center flex flex-col gap-4 animate-on-scroll">
            <span class="text-3xl mx-auto">{lic.icon}</span>
            <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">{lic.name}</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm flex-1 leading-relaxed">{lic.desc}</p>
            <a
              href={lic.href}
              target={lic.external ? '_blank' : undefined}
              rel={lic.external ? 'noopener' : undefined}
              class="btn-outline-teal !text-sm justify-center"
            >
              {lic.cta}
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
